Who am I?

Hair Color: Blonde

Eye Color: Hazel

Siblings: 1 brother 17

School: Riverside Community College soon to be Cal state Fullerton

Hobbies: Dancing, Jazz Tap Ballet Modern lyrical, u name it lol. I love clubbing and shopping too!

Sports that you play/enjoy: Dance and i am a songleader at rcc

Height: 5Â’6 1/2 =)

Best Friends: My trupletas, Teresa, Kristin and Jessica

Good Friends: Heather, Sarah, Alex, Stephanie, Heather

Celebrities that I've met: Nick Carter 10 times, Aj Mclean 4 times, Kevin Richardson 1 times, Howie Durough 1 time (no brian yet) Mandy Moore 1 time, Missy Elliot 1 time, Trevor from Otown 2 times, Celion Dion 1 time. I think thats it.

Favorites

Favorite Color: maroon dark, green and black

Favorite Quote: "Let's go and get hot and sweaty playing ball, then we can come back here and get a lil more hot and sweaty"

2nd Favorite Quote: "Dude i told ya so dawg"

Favorite Song: As Long As You Love Me>>>BAckstreet Boys

Favorite Band: BSB...The one and only Best...BAckstreet Boys....and then Linkin Park

Favorite Solo Singer: Nick Carter!

Favorite Lotion/perfume Scent: Clinique Happy, Estee LAuder PLeasures and Victoria Secrets Pink

Favorite Drink: Coca cola....Do you smell coke? lol

Favorite Food: PIZZA

A LiL info about me:

** I started dancing at 3 1/2 years old. I took jazz tap ballet and lyrical. Continuted dancing for 16 years of my life. I was also a cheerleader and songleader throughout high school....being captain 3 out of the 4 years i attended =) (not too many people can say that!)hehe Then i joined the dance program at Rcc and i am currently on their cheer/dance team until i transfer to Cal state Fullerton where i will continue dance over there. Right now i am currently teaching at 2 dance studios, and choreographing for their competition teams. My ultimate Dream is to become a backup dancer in the music industry and maybe a laker girl! Ive come very close, so we will see what happens !! =)

*I love my parents to death, i love em i love em i love em!!! They are a very important part in my life.

** I am A pop princes when it comes to music. I love POP music and im not afraid to admit it lol. I love the backstreet boys obviously, Britney Spears, Christina Aguilera, Mandy Moore, all the pop artists except for....... Nsync lol i dontlike Nsync

~~ My Personality: I am sooooo easy to get along with cuz i am always happy lol. Sometimes, well rarley i will be serious if i have to be, but besides that i am the hugest goofball there is =)

Last Comment>>>>>> I Love the Backstreet Boys!
